{"tid":2199639,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"微軟雲遊戲服務下周二推出 月費15美元","createTime":"2020-09-12T11:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T14:30:25.000Z","uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c21c762fc11b04012a455a88b5d211234af71d","tid":2199639,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"微軟（美︰MSFT）宣布，將於下周二（15日）推出雲遊戲服務「Xbox Game Pass Ultimate」<strong>，其中新用戶第一個月只收取1美元的費用</strong>。微軟此舉要是為了吸引休閒遊戲玩家，同時令Xbox更好地應對來自索尼（美︰SNE）Play Station5的競爭。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，微軟的雲遊戲服務每月正式月費為14.99美元，用戶可以通過Xbox遊戲主機、Android設備和電腦，通過網絡連接遊玩150多款熱門遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，Google已推出了雲遊戲平台Stadia ，雲遊戲領域的競爭日趨白熱化。但由於，事實上Stadia支援的遊戲數目有限，未能掀起熱潮。另外，英偉達（美︰NVDA）亦已發布了雲遊戲平台GeForce Now。"},{"pid":"9d8f36a856092c8c22befd8866736fdd1e1c5a25","tid":2199639,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"nvda ?<br />\nnvidia ?"},{"pid":"5cb4993e9e94d525199e73880eeeb50ae33f67fa","tid":2199639,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:15:18.000Z","msg":"香港有？"},{"pid":"019f37d9c1f03ee7992c96e9aa34126068e66795","tid":2199639,"uid":176661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:16:39.000Z","msg":"之前唔係話佢地聯手打google嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c5be1b7f5d378fe67c300d21172347414ee124","tid":2199639,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:16:39.000Z","msg":"咁多間都抄ps plus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />EA前排先出咗"},{"pid":"fc9eb52836cddb13df205e76c29d1830bcaac99a","tid":2199639,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:17:53.000Z","msg":"香港無份啦"},{"pid":"c6b4252e47585febe3a734b51e745c7d11fca816","tid":2199639,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d8f36a856092c8c22befd8866736fdd1e1c5a25","tid":2199639,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":